{"id": "art-117", "label": "Art. 117", "title": "Art. 117", "slug": "art-117", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 117 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1036810406\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2325\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1036810406\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Adunarea general&#259; este convocat&#259; de consiliul\nde <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv de directorat, ori\nde câte ori este necesar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2073739104\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2324\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2073739104\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Termenul de întrunire nu poate fi mai mic de 30 de zile\nde la publicarea convoc&#259;rii în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea a\nIV-a.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_684391661\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2323\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_684391661\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Convocarea se public&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al\nRomâniei, Partea a IV-a, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în unul dintre\nziarele de larg&#259; r&#259;spândire din localitatea în care se afl&#259;\nsediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> sau din cea mai\napropiat&#259; localitate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2124129097\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2322\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2124129097\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Convocarea poate fi f&#259;cut&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nnumai prin scrisoare recomandat&#259; sau, dac&#259; actul constitutiv permite,\nprin scrisoare transmis&#259; pe cale electronic&#259;, semnat&#259; cu o\nsemn&#259;tur&#259; electronic&#259; calificat&#259; sau semn&#259;tur&#259;\nelectronic&#259; avansat&#259;, expediat&#259;, cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n30 de zile înainte de data <span class=SpellE>&#355;inerii</span>\nadun&#259;rii, la adresa <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarului</span>,\nînscris&#259; în registrul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.\nSchimbarea adresei nu poate fi opus&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\ndac&#259; nu i-a fost comunicat&#259; în scris de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_990522399\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2321\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_990522399\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Modurile de convocare prev&#259;zute la alin. (4) nu pot\nfi folosite dac&#259; sunt interzise prin actul constitutiv al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> sau prin <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ii</span>\nlegale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2070681679\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2320\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2070681679\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Convocarea va cuprinde locul <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ndata <span class=SpellE>&#355;inerii</span> adun&#259;rii, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ordinea de zi, cu <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionarea</span>\nexplicit&#259; a tuturor problemelor care vor face obiectul dezbaterilor\nadun&#259;rii. În cazul în care pe ordinea de zi figureaz&#259; numirea\nadministratorilor sau a membrilor consiliului de supraveghere, în convocare se\nva <span class=SpellE>men&#355;iona</span> c&#259; lista cuprinzând <span\nclass=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> cu privire la numele, localitatea de\ndomiciliu <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> calificarea profesional&#259; ale\npersoanelor propuse pentru <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ia</span> de\nadministrator se afl&#259; la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, putând fi consultat&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> completat&#259; de <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>.</span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'> În cazul în care se asigur&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nparticiparea prin mijloace electronice de comunicare la <span class=SpellE>distan&#355;&#259;</span>,\nconvocatorul cuprinde <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> descrierea procedurilor\ncare trebuie urmate de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span> pentru a\nparticipa <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> vota online în adunarea\ngeneral&#259;.</span></u><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1096385483\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2319\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1096385483\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Când pe ordinea de zi figureaz&#259; propuneri pentru\nmodificarea actului constitutiv, convocarea va trebui s&#259; cuprind&#259;\ntextul integral al propunerilor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_44718914\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2318\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_44718914\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Pentru <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nlistate se aplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> relevante\ndin <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span> specific&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>pie&#355;ei</span> de capital.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}